---
description: Run Holo QA for UI-facing changes in Nimbus Desk
globs:
  - "src/**/*.jsx"
  - "qa/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

For UI-facing changes, follow `AGENTS.md`.

Use the `holo-qa` MCP tools. If they are unavailable, stop and report that the
Holo QA tools are unavailable.

Implement the requested change before hunting unrelated existing bugs. Use Holo
QA as the UI evidence, then make at most one minimal fix and re-run the same
spec once.
